Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.09,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Hang in there! Are you okay?}Này! Ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.20,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.19,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I'll probably heal... sooner or later?}Tớ sẽ khỏi thôi... chờ chút...
