Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:27.87,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{Then there's that old man who has\N my grandfather and his friends' memories...}Còn lão già mang kí ức của ông ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.13,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{What in the world is going on?}Rốt cuộc thế giới này bị gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.71,Main,Peanut gallery A,0,0,0,,{What's with all the cops?}Sao lại có cảnh sát?
