Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.36,Main,Peanut gallery D,0,0,0,,{Oh, my. How dreadful.}Thật kinh khủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.84,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Looks like the experiment's a success...}Có vẻ thí nghiệm đã thành công...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:45.97,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What is it, you old hag?}Gì nữa bà già?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.08,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What in the world is going on?}Thế giới này rốt cuộc là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.61,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I demand an explanation!}Giải thích đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.73,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{From me?}Tôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:59.02,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Say, Cory-kun, could you not squeeze those?}Nè Cory... đừng có bóp vú tớ nữa.
