Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.84,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry.}X-xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.15,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{It's kind of making my wound hurt.}Nó làm tớ đau đó.
