Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.93,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Is that all? Then I've got another question.}Thế à? Vậy ta có câu hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.55,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{There was a man in that fight\Nwho had my grandfather's memories.}Có một ông già mang kí ức của ông ta,
