Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.68,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's like everything she touches\N turns into a problem.}Bất kể mọi thứ cô ta nhúng tay vào đều phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.44,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Why don't you head to bed, General Piscalat?}Đi ngủ đi, chỉ huy Piscalat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.00,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I appreciate your concern,}Tôi rất cảm ơn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.70,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{but after working with you over these \Nyears and never seeing you rest,}nhưng sau từng ấy năm làm việc,\N tôi chưa thấy cậu ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.21,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{the idea of taking time for \Nmyself is a bit disheartening.}Dành thời gian cho riêng tôi thì thật không đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.68,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Considering our physiological differences, \Nthat's just the way it is.}Khác biệt về thần kinh mà, chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.71,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I'll see you later, okay?}Gặp cô sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.06,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Yes... In that case, \Nmaybe I'll take your suggestion.}Vâng... Vậy thì tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.61,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{He's pretty incredible...}Thật khó tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.30,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{being able to work effectively\N without ever resting.}có thể làm việc hiệu quả mà không cần nghỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.87,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{And unlike every other man I've worked with,}Và không như những tên đàn\N ông mình từng làm việc cùng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.97,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{we've been alone for long periods of time\N and he's never tried anything.}dù ở bên nhau rất lâu mà \Ncậu ấy chưa từng có ý gì với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.91,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I almost wish he would...}Đáng ra phải mạnh dạn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.61,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Wait, no, no! What am I thinking?!}Không, không! Mình nghĩ cái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.88,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{Is something wrong, General Piscalat?}Có chuyện gì sao, chỉ huy Piscalat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.69,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{Wh-What is it?}S-Sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.24,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}I-Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.65,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I'm just tired!}Ta chỉ hơi mệt thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.82,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{That's right! It's just exhaustion!}Đúng thế! Chỉ mệt mỏi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.95,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{That has to be it!}Chính là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.30,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I'm going to get a few hours' rest.}Phải nghỉ ngơi vài tiếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.22,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Interrupt and you're in for an execution!}Vào phá là tử hình đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.33,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{R-Right... Rest well, ma'am.}V-Vâng... chúc ngủ ngon thưa ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.84,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,1780)\pos(322.667,38.667)\fnArial\fs16\c&H6E6434&\b1\3c&HAEA171&\4c&HAEA171&}{Shower Room}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.84,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,1780)\fnComic Sans MS\frz-15\fs16\c&H1F646F&\b1\3c&H96DCF0&\4c&HCAEFFC&\pos(359.334,206.667)}{Stay out!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.84,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{I think maybe now's a good time...}Quá đúng lúc...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.23,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{If we're not certain what the enemy is up to,}Nếu không biết kẻ thù đang định làm gì,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.18,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{then for now, we'll have to simply get \Nstrong enough to erase any doubts!}thì chúng ta chỉ cần mạnh mẽ hơn để xóa sổ mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:26.15,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,{Ugh... she's just gone back to her old self.}Thiệt tình... lại trở về là bà già cũ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:31.40,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Do I really need to stick around if the \Nmonster lady is back in the equation?}Tôi có cần phải theo dõi bà già quái vật đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.71,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Hey, speak of the devil. \NThere's my recall order.}Cơ mà mình có lệnh rút lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.54,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Paula-chan, there's no real \Npoint in me sticking around,}Paula-chan, không còn lý do gì tôi ở đây nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.96,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{so I'm heading back to Zoble.}nên quay về Zoble đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.67,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Okay. Have a safe trip.}Ừm, đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:50.67,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{They want me to bring you along.\N Didn't say why.}Họ muốn tôi mang cậu đi cùng. Không rõ tại sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.00,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Really? I'll go.}Vậy à? Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.93,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{And then hopefully I won't \Nhave to come back...}Hi vọng không phải quay lại đây nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.46,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Is the ventilation busted?}Hệ thống thông gió có vấn đề à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.23,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{The steam isn't dissipating at all.}Hơi nước không biến mất?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.69,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I'll have the idiot who's \Nresponsible executed later.}Tí nữa phải xử tên quản lý vụ này mới được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.33,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Damn it all...}Chết tiệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.95,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Th-This is...}Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.38,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{It's... the same drug... from before...}Là... loại thuốc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.24,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{B-But who?}Nhưng kẻ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.22,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Impossible... How?}Không thể nào...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.38,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I should be the only one \Nwho can get in here.}Đáng ra chỉ có mình mới vào được đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:38.64,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{Yeah, these chemicals definitely seem to \Nhave an immediate effect on human brains.}Những chất này ảnh hưởng ngay lập tức lên não bộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.90,Italics,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{A regular soldier? How?!}Binh nhất? Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.64,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Y-You wretch... D-Don't think you'll...}N-Ngươi... ngươi nghĩ mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.13,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Don't look...}Đừng nhìn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.54,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{It's nothing to be embarrassed about,\N Piscalat, my dear.}Không có gì xấu hổ cả, Piscalat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.90,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{I've already seen you in the nude \Nduring your physicals, haven't I?}Ta đã thấy ngươi khỏa thân bao nhiêu lần rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.16,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I-Is that you... Your Lordship?}L-Là... Quỷ vương?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.27,Main,Pete/Obami,0,0,0,,{Mechanical bodies are quite convenient.}Cơ thể máy khá thuận thiện nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.28,Main,Pete/Obami,0,0,0,,{They let you impersonate whoever you want.}Có thể giúp ta trở thành bất cứ ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:15.55,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{The demon sightings have all been \Nin the radius of this area...}Những con quỷ bị phát hiện đều ở trong khu vực này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.43,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{And General Piscalat is late.}Cơ mà Piscalat lâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.73,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Maybe she's actually getting\N some decent sleep for once.}Có lẽ lâu không ngủ nên ngủ hơi nhiều à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.07,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Sorry to keep you waiting.}Xin lỗi vì đã để ngài chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:31.19,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I was wondering... \Nwhere is Prontea-san right now?}Tôi tự hỏi... Prontea đang ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:35.02,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Prontea-san? Right now he should be \Nin the vicinity of the Gaina Coast}Prontea? Chắc đang ở bờ biển Gaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.61,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{looking for Raki and Kroft—}Tìm Raki và Kroft--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:42.45,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I see. That's all I need to know,\N you piece of shit!}Vậy à? Vậy là đủ rồi, tên khốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.60,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. You won't die just yet.}Đừng lo, ta sẽ không giết ngươi ngay đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.34,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't be satisfied\N letting you off that easy.}Chỉ thế thì chưa đủ thỏa mãn cho ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.50,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear... Was it something \NI said, Piscalat-chan?}Ôi chà, có chuyện gì thế Piscalat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.47,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{This is bad. Her brainwashing's \Nbeen completely undone.}Tệ quá. Hết bị tẩy não rồi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:04.11,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{What's wrong? Did you \Nimplant a bomb in my body?}Sao thế? Định cho nổ quả bom trong cơ thể ta à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:07.97,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{You think you're gonna blow the place? \NOr make an emergency call to Prontea?}Ngươi muốn cho nổ tung nơi này? Hay gọi cho Prontea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.48,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Too bad you can't do any of that}Thật tệ khi ngươi chẳng thể làm gì
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.73,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{if the gizmos you hide \Nin your body won't work.}nếu thứ ngươi giấu trong cơ thể không hoạt động.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.48,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{How? Why aren't they working?}Sao chúng không hoạt động?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:20.74,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{You see, when all electrical devices are \Ndisabled, you can't use any of them.}Tất cả thiết bị điện đã bị vô hiệu hóa rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.10,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,Pete?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.24,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{No... the Demon Lord!}Không... Quỷ vương à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.37,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I see. So that was you.}Ra là vậy. Lúc đó là ngươi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.50,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{You switched faces and clothing at the store—}Đổi mặt và thay đồ trong khu mua sắm--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.71,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{Correct you are.}Đúng rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:34.00,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{And if you had caught on sooner, \Nthis entire plan would have been scrapped.}Và nếu ngươi bắt ta sớm thì đã không có chuyện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.40,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Looks like the Demon Lord's \Npulled it off, Merku.}Có vẻ Ma vương đã thành công rồi Merku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:43.76,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{I see. Does that mean my skin-suit crafting \Nlife has finally come to an end?}Vậy à? Vậy là không cần phải lột da để giả dạng nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.27,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{Granted...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:50.31,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{I thought I was done for when \Nhe peeked in on the changing room.}ta tưởng đã xong khi bị hắn\N nhìn qua phòng thay đồ rồi cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:54.34,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That implies one of the customers \Nreacted to Prontea-san searching...}Vậy là Prontea đã bỏ qua à...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.52,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{How could he have not noticed that?! Damn it!}Sao không nhận ra chứ, chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.53,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I see you're both back.}Hai người quay lại rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:09.23,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Let's get to business, Paula. \NYou're to join Ysley-dono.}Làm việc thôi Paula. Sẽ tham gia cùng Ysley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.50,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Cory, you were recalled\N because your job on the island is done.}Cory, cậu được gọi về vì hết việc ở đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.75,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Why not grab something to eat?}Sao không kiếm gì ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:19.96,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Piscalat-neechan said there wouldn't\Nbe any missions any time soon,}Chị Piscalat nói không có nhiệm vụ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.13,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{but I'm betting I'll be sent to help \NProntea-san hunt wild demons—}nhưng chắc lại chuẩn bị đưa mình tới chỗ Prontea--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.85,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{H-Huh? I'm getting... sleepy...}Ủa? Buồn ngủ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.22,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{I appreciate how straightforward\N you are, Cory.}Cory dễ dụ thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:39.32,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{Being asleep will make \Nthe procedure a lot smoother.}Ngủ sẽ giúp loại bỏ tẩy não dễ dàng hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.57,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Paula!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:47.07,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Where did she go? There's no sign\N of her coming back, either.}Con bé đâu rồi? Sao không quay lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.33,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Maybe you kicked her ass too hard this time.}Tại bà già đánh mạnh quá nên cậu ta trốn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.13,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I have to agree that Rin-san's training \Ncan be a bit overly severe at times.}Tôi cũng đồng ý với cậu là Rin-san khắc nghiệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:54.58,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Yep.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.20,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{She seems to have headed \Nto Zoble along with Cory-san...}Có vẻ đi cùng Cory quay về Zoble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.84,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'll ask about it.}Tôi gọi điện hỏi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.41,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{You've mastered those human tools, then?!}Cô dùng thiết bị của loài người hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:10.84,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{So you're one of those \Negghead types like Ysley?!}Là kiểu đầu óc như Ysley à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.10,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?\N It's just a cell phone.}Nói gì thế? Chỉ là điện thoại thôi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.10,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But... Huh? No answer.}Hả? Không nhấc máy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.61,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Is that you, Gill-chan?}Gill-chan hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.32,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{It's sure rare for you to dial me up!}Hiếm lắm mới gọi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.19,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.92,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{You're wondering where she is?}Đang ở đâu á?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:26.53,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I haven't heard, actually.\N You're better off asking Ysley-kun...}Không biết nữa. Cô hỏi Ysley đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.49,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Wait, what?}Khoan đã, cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:38.83,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{We should never lose communications\Nwith the command center!}Chúng ta đáng ra không được mất liên lạc với trụ sở chính.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.65,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,Ysley! Piscalat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.05,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Damn it...}Chết tiệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.59,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{They got us!\N But who actually attacked and how?}Chúng trên cơ rồi! Kẻ nào đã tấn công?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.85,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I can't imagine Ysley-kun and General Piscalat\N losing if they were together.}Không thể tin là Ysley và chỉ huy Piscalat\N lại thua khi bên cạnh nhau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.56,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{And even against an overwhelming opponent,}Và dù đối thủ có mạnh cỡ nào,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.21,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I think he'd probably abandon her to flee.}thì cậu ta chỉ cần bỏ rơi cô ta là được mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.88,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{I'd say we finished up in the nick of time.}Có vẻ đã đến đúng giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.70,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Say, Your Lordship,}Nè Quỷ vương,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.41,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{what would you have done if undoing\Nmy brainwashing had taken another 30 minutes?}quá trình tẩy não tôi mà chậm 30 phút thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.29,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{Die, most likely.}Chắc hẳn là chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.33,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Damn it... They really got us!}Chết tiệt... Chúng đi trước một bước rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.92,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Should I be more angry or worried?}Giờ nên tức giận hay lo lắng đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:24.92,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Who is it?! What do you want?!}Ai thế? Muốn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:30.14,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{What's all this? I couldn't \Nget in touch with Piscalat or Ysley,}Gì là sao? Tôi không thể liên lạc với Piscalat lẫn Ysley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.68,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{and now I hear command's \Nbeen blown up or something.}Và giờ nghe báo cáo trụ sở bị đánh bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.68,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Neput? What are you doing right now?}Neput? Ông đang làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.31,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{Working on the treaties and \Nother paperwork to establish}Làm mấy cái hiệp ước và công việc bàn giấy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.09,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{diplomatic crap with Hotaena and Sarabael.}ngoại giao với Hotaena và Sarabael.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.33,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{That doesn't matter! \NI need you here! Right now!}Kệ chuyện đó đi! Đến đây ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.69,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{No, I'll come to you!}Không, tôi sẽ đến đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.28,Main,Barcode,0,0,0,,{Has something happened?}Có chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.67,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{Not sure exactly, but it's probably bad news.}Ai biết, nhưng tình hình tệ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.41,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{That damn Miku is always a pain in the \Nass when you get on her bad side.}Chắc chắn Miku lại bày trò gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.29,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{I'd say this was basically \Nthe best possible result.}Tuy không phải kết quả lý tưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:02.04,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{We were able to recover Piscalat and Cory, \Nand the enemy isn't aware of that yet.}Nhưng chúng ta đã lấy lại Piscalat và\N Cory, kẻ địch thì vẫn đang rối rắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.54,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{So, what shall we do next?}Giờ làm gì nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.29,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Let's see...}Xem nào..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.59,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{For now... let's not make any moves.}Đừng di chuyển nữa nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.42,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Oh, no, not you! You should \Nkeep moving even harder, okay?}Không không phải em! Em cứ mạnh hơn nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.51,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Phải nhỉ..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.58,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{We managed to collect two Idaten samples.}Chúng ta đã có 2 Idaten làm mẫu vật.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:23.52,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Why not spend some time studying them?\N At a nice, leisurely pace.}Tại sao không nghiên cứu chúng nhỉ? Từ từ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.52,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Now then...}Giờ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.84,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Do you understand what's about to happen?}Ngươi có hiểu chuyện gì sẽ xảy ra không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.28,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{How about you, missy?}Cô bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.78,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I kind of think we might die...}Chắc chúng ta sẽ chết?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.65,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{You think you're gonna die, huh?}Chết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.29,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{That's a cute answer.}Câu trả lời dễ thương đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.77,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{But for now, the physical exam comes first.}Nhưng đầu tiên kiểm tra cơ thể trước đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:46.64,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{For example, what's going on in here?!}Ví dụ như thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.41,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,{Oh, torture.}Tra tấn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.01,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,{Aw, man, this is probably gonna hurt a lot.}Thiệt tình, đau quá cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.50,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{You're gonna learn there are \Nthings worse than death...}Ta sẽ bắt ngươi sống không bằng chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.01,Italics,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{She's not screaming?}Không la?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.50,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Ouchie!}Đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.48,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Hey, don't kill her.}Này, đừng có giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.85,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Quit trying to act tough, you little shit.}Đừng có ra vẻ cứng rắn, con ranh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.66,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Yeowch! Ouch, ouch, ouch...}Đau, đau đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.48,Italics,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Why the hell isn't she \Nscreaming her head off?}Cái tiếng la chết tiệt gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.87,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{You're next.}Tiếp theo là mày.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.11,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{I don't think a regular rectal \Nprobe is gonna cut it for you.}Tao không nghĩ dao thường sẽ cắt nổi mày.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:18.24,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll slice you open \Nfrom your intestines to your throat.}Giờ thử rạch từ cổ họng xuống xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:21.50,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{His mouth, too. Pull all those teeth out.}Mồm nữa, rút hết răng nó ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:26.40,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{No, maybe rip his entire face off\Nstarting with his eyes.}Không, lột toàn bộ da mặt và móc mắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.28,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Those're some sweet sounds you're making!}Nghe hay đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.91,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Our flesh returns to the earth,\N and our souls to the Lord's side.}Xác thịt quay về với đất mẹ, linh hồn về với thiên đàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:41.97,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Please look over us, who inherit Your works.}Xin hãy dõi theo chúng con. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:45.38,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{That concludes the prayer for the dead,}Đây là lời cầu nguyện cho người đã khuất,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.52,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{but was it really all right \Nto use rites from my country?}nhưng sử dụng nghi lễ của nước tôi liệu có ổn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.90,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{It's okay, sister.}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.42,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{The important thing isn't the ritual itself,}Quan trọng  không phải nghi thức,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.72,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{but rather nurturing the belief that \Nthe dead should be honored.}mà luôn tin rằng người chết phải được tôn vinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.91,Main,Pete,0,0,0,,{I realize I'm not in any position to ask\Nsuch a thing from you, but...}Tôi nghĩ mình không có tư cách để nhờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:06.04,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{No. This is all I can really do, so...}Không, đây là chuyện duy nhất tôi có thể làm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:12.42,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Besides, lately, I've begun to question \Nwhat's truly good or evil.}Hơn nữa, gần đây tôi cũng tự hỏi thần linh hay ác quỷ là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.80,Flashback,Prontea,0,0,0,,{You think we should make \Npeace with the demons?}Cô nghĩ sẽ sống hòa bình với ác quỷ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.86,Flashback,Gill+,0,0,0,,{I do! If we don't have to fight, \Nwouldn't we be better if we didn't?}Phải! Nếu không chiến đấu với nhau,\N thì chẳng phải tốt hơn sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:22.02,Flashback,Gill,0,0,0,,{They were worried about my well being.}Họ đã lo lắng về sức khỏe của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.30,Flashback,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm sure we can come to an \Nunderstanding if we just talk.}Thế nên nhất định nếu nói chuyện sẽ hiểu được nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.86,Flashback,Protnea,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's do that.}Vậy thì làm thế đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.97,Flashback,Protnea,0,0,0,,{But in that case,}Nhưng trước đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.07,Flashback,Protnea,0,0,0,,{we're going to need thousands of human babies}chúng ta cần hàng ngàn em bé nhân loại
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.82,Flashback,Protnea,0,0,0,,{in order to maintain the demon population.}để duy trì dân số cho ác quỷ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.65,Flashback,Gill,0,0,0,,{That's...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.57,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Out of the question?}Không thể à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.12,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{In that case, the demons will have \Nto be prohibited from reproducing}Vậy chúng ta sẽ cấm quỷ sinh sản
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.08,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{until they die out from natural causes.}cho đến khi chúng chết vì nguyên nhân tự nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.78,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{What you're suggesting in that case\N isn't a compromise.}Những gì cô đề xuất không phải thỏa hiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.93,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's a one-sided death sentence.}Mà là bản án tử dành cho một bên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.58,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{The only path to peace \Nis finding a way for Idaten, humans,}Con đường hòa bình duy nhất cho Idaten, nhân loại,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.19,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{and demons to all be satisfied.}và ác quỷ, tất cả đều hài lòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.46,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Is everybody here, Your Lordship?}Mọi người ở đây ạ, Quỷ vương?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.18,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{Indeed.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.72,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{It's a rundown farm, but there \Nare facilities underground.}Phía trên là trang trại nhưng dưới là cơ sở nghiên cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.39,Main,Obami/Pete,0,0,0,,{We'll conduct the experiments \Non the Idaten here, as well.}Bọn ta đang thí nghiệm Idaten ở dưới đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.10,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'd love to help with that part.}Tôi vui được giúp đỡ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.88,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{I've got some pretty personal \Ngrudges against them.}Tôi có vài mối thù với chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.49,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey, Cory. It's been a while.}Này Cory, đã lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.74,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Cory-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.70,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{According to the deities, in Zoble,}Theo các vị thần trong Zoble,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:33.72,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{the demons were attempting to mass-produce \Nhumans that they could fuse with demons.}những con ác quỷ đang cố gắng tăng\N dân số bằng việc hợp nhất nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.45,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{They were just desperate to ensure \Nthe survival of their species...}Chúng chỉ tuyệt vọng để duy trì nòi giống...
