Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.73,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and heal. \NThen I'll get to cutting again.}Nhanh trị thương đi để ta còn làm tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:52.23,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{We'll change the type of pain\N over and over again...}Bọn ta sẽ liên tiếp khiến các ngươi đau đớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.89,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Hey. Sorry, Cory, looks like the \Nexperiments for today are...}Xin lỗi nhé Cory, thí nghiệm hôm nay hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:59.22,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{What's wrong? You look kind of sick.}Sao thế? Xanh xao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:03.31,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah... Probably because my \Nbrainwashing was just undone.}À... ảnh hưởng tẩy não chưa hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.30,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Guess I'm kinda tired, you know?}Có vẻ tôi vẫn còn mệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:09.00,Italics,Cory,0,0,0,,{What is this? The brainwashing was undone...}Cái gì thế này? Cứ tưởng đã hết bị tẩy não...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.13,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should get some sleep.}Mình nên ngủ chút thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.13,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{It hurts... It hurts...}Đau quá... đau quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.67,Main,Kuraishi,0,0,0,,{Well, it's your turn to keep watch.}Vậy nhờ cô canh chừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.76,Main,Ferlandia,0,0,0,,{You got it.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.76,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,{So, based on the information \NI got from Piscalat,}Dựa theo thông tin từ Piscalat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.44,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,{the Demon Lord is practically \Nconfirmed to be an Idaten}Quỷ vương có danh tính là Idaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.79,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,{who came into existence \Non the other side of the seal.}thực thể hóa từ phong ấn bên kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.12,Main,Umeyo,0,0,0,,{I'm so bored...}Chán quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.52,Main,Umeyo,0,0,0,,{Could one of you two get pregnant already?}Hai người mang thai được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.40,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{And what am I supposed to do differently?}Dù có nói thế thì cũng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.90,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{From a human perspective,\Nit's easy to condemn what they do.}Ở góc độ nhân loại, chúng ta không thể đồng cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.91,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But as a mere fellow living thing, I can't.}Nhưng trên góc độ sinh vật sống thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.62,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{A way for all of our species to coexist...}Một cách để tất cả có thể cùng chung sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.69,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I can't imagine how to get there,}Tôi vẫn chưa thể nghĩ ra,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:54.36,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{but... is there really no compromise at all?}nhưng... không lẽ không có sao?
