Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.63,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Who got them?!}Ai bắt chúng?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.73,Main,Gill+,0,0,0,,{I don't know.}Tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.69,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Where do we go to save them?!}Cứu chúng ở đâu?
